# sm3utils

SM3 Cryptographic Hash Algorithm.

## Install

```
pip install sm3utils
```

## Usage

```
from sm3utils import sm3

gen = sm3()
gen.update(b'abc')
result = gen.hexdigest()
print("result=", result)

# result= 66c7f0f462eeedd9d1f2d46bdc10e4e24167c4875cf2f7a2297da02b8f4ba8e0
```
